starring tomas milian and manny perez  'washington heights' is a low budget drama set in a latino neighborhood in nyc.a young comic-book artist (manny perez) wants to escape his latino neighborhood. when his father is crippled by a robber's gunshot, the young man is forced to run the family bodega.the movie was shot in a budget (low resolution video and poor audio) with low profile actors.the plot flowed well for 85 minutes but the last 5 minutes were just terrible. we don't know for sure if perez and his girlfriend remained together and if angel ended-up in jail for the shooting.4/10

